The effort required to generate the crafted input required to exploit this issue is complex and requires significant effort before a successful attack can be expected.

item.title: CVE-2023-25839|2023-07-19T15:45:47.077Z -- esri -- arcgis%20insights
item.description: There is SQL injection vulnerability in Esri ArcGIS Insights Desktop for Mac and Windows version 2022.1 that may allow a local, authorized attacker to execute arbitrary SQL commands against the back-end database. The effort required to generate the crafted input required to exploit this issue is complex and requires significant effort before a successful attack can be expected.
